#: ../../source/library/models/opinions/HK.rst:5
#: f967a1aac6f14729a66763783e96b00a
msgid ""
"The HK model [1]_ describes continuous opinion dynamics. Each node holds an "
"initial opinion :math:`h \\in [-1,1]` and updates it in discrete rounds. At "
"each step: 1) :math:`\\epsilon` neighbor identification: find the set "
":math:`\\Gamma_\\epsilon` of each node, :math:`d_{i,j}=\\left|h_i-"
"h_j\\right|\\le\\epsilon`, :math:`j\\in\\Gamma_\\epsilon`; 2) update the "
"opinion value: The opinion of node :math:`i` at the next time step is "
"updated as follows:"
msgstr ""
"HK模式[1] 描述持续舆论动态. 每个节点都有一个初步意见:`h \\ in [-1,1]',并用离散的回合加以更新。 每一步:1) : : : "
"math: `\\epsilon ' 邻居识别: 找到集: math: `\\: `\\amma \\epsilon' 每个节点, : math: `d"
" {i, j}=\\left|h i-h j\\right|\\le\\epsilon', : math: j\\in\\Gamma "
"\\epsilon'; 2) 更新观点值: 节点: mmath: `i' 在下一个步骤更新如下:"

#: ../../source/library/models/opinions/HK.rst:12
#: bfb5b6d2c9d447ce936682bd6aabd5b7
msgid ""
"h_i^{\\left(k\\right)}=\\frac{\\sum_{j\\in\\Gamma_\\epsilon}{h_j^{\\left(k-1\\right)}}}{\\#\\Gamma_\\epsilon}"
msgstr "左 右 右 右 右 右 右 右 右"

#: ../../source/library/models/opinions/HK.rst:17
#: 1816e1ca765f467ca53f1457ce3ab5ce
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\#\\Gamma_\\epsilon` denotes the number of :math:`\\epsilon` "
"neighbors."
msgstr "其中: math:QQGamma \\epsilon`表示:math:`\\epsilon'的邻居人数."

